            "code": "// Simple LED Blink Circuit\n// Red LED on pin 13 with 220Ω resistor\n\nvoid setup() {\n  // Configure pin 13 as an output\n  pinMode(13, OUTPUT);\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  // Turn the LED on\n  digitalWrite(13, HIGH);\n  delay(1000);  // Wait 1 second (1000 milliseconds)\n  \n  // Turn the LED off\n  digitalWrite(13, LOW);\n  delay(1000);  // Wait 1 second\n}\n"
